Program: Omnibus
Title: The Day Apartheid Died - Soweto Uprising
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p0376lhc
Last Broadcast Date: 02 July 1997
Memories of the day on June 16th 1976 when secondary students in Soweto protesting against forced tuition in Afrikaans were fired on by South African authorities. Contributors include Tsietsi Mashinini, protest organiser.